  "text": "[ ] where {HS} is the mass concentration of the humic substance in g/dm [CITATION_1] , and m is the number of functional groups binding a europium ion and is assumed to be 3, which is equal to the charge number of Eu 3+ in the present study. When complex EuL is formed with each binding site, the three proton-exchanging groups are assigned to be formally satisfied with a charge-neutralized complex. Then, Equation (8) ",
